issue.body:
Updates the requirements on [vimeo/psalm](https://github.com/vimeo/psalm) to permit the latest version.
Release notes

Sourced from vimeo/psalm's releases.

Mostly bugfixes

Features

  • @‚Äãweirdan added support for PHP Version-dependent method stubs (#5337)

Bugfixes

  • Improving handling of nested template types in class strings (#5290)
  • Language Server Allow static methods to be autocompleted on instances (#5210, #5295)
  • Language Server Fix inferred type caching bug when editing neighbouring methods (#5297)
  • Fix JSON reports containing UTF-8 strings ‚Äì thanks @‚Äãdanog (#5300)
  • Improve callmap for gd functions in PHP 8 ‚Äì thanks @‚Äãiluuu1994 (#5271)
  • improvements to mysql_init and PDOStatement::fetchAll return type ‚Äì thanks @‚Äãmorozov (#5306, #5317)
  • WeakMap is now generic ‚Äì thanks @‚Äãweirdan (#5313)
  • Allow iterable coercion from a generic object (#5310)
  • Fix an issue with method memoisation (#5317)
  • Allow ReflectionParameter::getType() to return non-null if a ReflectionParameter::hasType() call returns true (#5258)
  • Undefined variables can now be tracked in arrow functions ‚Äì thanks @‚Äãweirdan (#5343)
  • ImplicitToStringCast is now emitted in more places ‚Äì thanks @‚Äãweirdan (#5344)
  • variable usage in bool to int casts are now tracked ‚Äì thanks @‚Äãweirdan (#5349)
  • explode return type is improved ‚Äì thanks @‚Äãweirdan (#5350)
  • ceil just returns a float, thanks @‚ÄãsimPod (#5355)
  • improved return type for min and max ‚Äì thanks @‚Äãorklah
  • Psalm startup variables are now shielded from plugins that change global variables ‚Äì thanks @‚Äãweirdan! (#5366)
  • fixed integer overflow that could cause a Psalm crash ‚Äì thanks @‚Äãorklah (#5369)
  • @‚Äãorklah fixed a bug where Psalm would not accurately type the output of array_map when given a callable (#5373)
  • prevented an edge-case where calling the constructor of a genericised class could poison Psalm's internal cache (b549989)

  • 205fdd1 Wrap entrypoints into IIFE to protect their variables (#5366)
  • 0a4ad57 add stubs for min/max (#5353)
  • 9793f92 Mark ceil() return type as float (#5355)
  • 5066377 Remove duplicate entry for 'amphp/amp' from composer.json file (#5352)
